  "summary": "Authentic Italian Pasta Carbonara is a classic dish from Rome made with eggs, hard cheese, cured pork, and black pepper. It's creamy but doesn't use cream, getting its richness from the eggs and cheese. This traditional Italian recipe is simple but absolutely delicious, requiring only a handful of ingredients.",
